code: /**  * A thin wrapper layer over {@link SplitStream#select(java.lang.String...)}.  *  * @param output_names The output names for which the operator will receive the  * input.  * @return Returns the selected {@link PythonDataStream}  */ public PythonDataStream select(String... output_names) {     return new PythonDataStream<>(this.stream.select(output_names)). }
